    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Sketch-Recognition"><a href="#Sketch-Recognition" class="headerlink" title="Sketch Recognition"></a>Sketch Recognition</h1><h2 id="1-论文"><a href="#1-论文" class="headerlink" title="1 论文"></a>1 论文</h2><h2 id="2-想法"><a href="#2-想法" class="headerlink" title="2 想法"></a>2 想法</h2><h3 id="2-1-连通域算法"><a href="#2-1-连通域算法" class="headerlink" title="2.1 连通域算法"></a>2.1 连通域算法</h3><h2 id="3-代码"><a href="#3-代码" class="headerlink" title="3 代码"></a>3 代码</h2><h3 id="3-1-连通域算法（Connected-Components-Labeling）"><a href="#3-1-连通域算法（Connected-Components-Labeling）" class="headerlink" title="3.1 连通域算法（Connected Components Labeling）"></a>3.1 连通域算法（Connected Components Labeling）</h3><p>通过对二值图像中目标像素的标记，让每个单独的连通区域形成一个被标识的块，进一步地获取这些块的轮廓、外接矩形、质心、不变矩阵等几何参数。</p>
<p>一个连通域是由具有相同像素值的相邻像素组成，对每个找到的连通域，赋予其一个唯一的标识（Label）以区别其他连通域。</p>
<p>基本算法：1）Two-pass 两遍扫描  2）Seed-Filling种子填充法</p>
<h3 id="3-2-膨胀操作"><a href="#3-2-膨胀操作" class="headerlink" title="3.2 膨胀操作"></a>3.2 膨胀操作</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> cv2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># no module named &quot;cv2&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># pip install python-opencv</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">img = cv2.imread(<span class="string">&#x27;408.png&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">cv_show</span>(<span class="params">img</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    cv2.imshow(<span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>, img)</span><br><span class="line">    cv2.waitKey(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    cv2.destroyAllWindows()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cv_show(img)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 黑底白字 膨胀操作</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># kernel = np.ones((3, 3), dtype=np.uint8)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># dilate = cv2.dilate(img, kernel, 1) # 1:迭代次数，也就是执行几次膨胀操作</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cv_show(dilate)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 黑底白字 腐蚀操作</span></span><br><span class="line">kernel = np.ones((<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">3</span>), dtype=np.uint8)</span><br><span class="line">erosion = cv2.erode(img, kernel, iterations=<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line">ss = np.hstack((img, erosion))</span><br><span class="line">cv_show(ss)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>





<h3 id="3-3-OpenCV取两张图像交集"><a href="#3-3-OpenCV取两张图像交集" class="headerlink" title="3.3 OpenCV取两张图像交集"></a>3.3 OpenCV取两张图像交集</h3><h2 id="4-BUG"><a href="#4-BUG" class="headerlink" title="4 BUG"></a>4 BUG</h2><h3 id="4-1-No-module-named-‘numpy’"><a href="#4-1-No-module-named-‘numpy’" class="headerlink" title="4.1 No module named ‘numpy’"></a>4.1 No module named ‘numpy’</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip3 install numpy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>





<h3 id="4-2-no-module-named-’cv2‘"><a href="#4-2-no-module-named-’cv2‘" class="headerlink" title="4.2 no module named ’cv2‘"></a>4.2 no module named ’cv2‘</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip3 install opencv-python</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># modulenotfounderror: no module named skbuild</span></span><br><span class="line">pip3 install --upgrade pip</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 然后再安装 opencv 即可</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>





<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 查看 opencv 版本</span><br><span class="line">pkg-config opencv --modversion</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>







]]></content>
