    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-Zerotier"><a href="#1-Zerotier" class="headerlink" title="1 Zerotier"></a>1 Zerotier</h1><p>官网：<a href="https://www.zerotier.com/">ZeroTier | Global Area Networking</a></p>
<p>Zerotier – 下载客户端并加入网络</p>
<p>Moon – 自建中转服务器</p>
<p>Linux-Ubuntu</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># install</span></span><br><span class="line">curl -s https://install.zerotier.com | sudo bash</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># zerotier command</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># start</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo zerotier-one -d</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># get the status of the server</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo zerotier-cli status</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># join the network</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo zerotier-cli <span class="built_in">join</span> 6ab565387af13fc7   <span class="comment"># Network-ID</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># cat other device</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo zerotier-cli listpeers </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># leave the network</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo zerotier-cli leave 6ab565387af13fc7 </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>





<h1 id="2-青龙"><a href="#2-青龙" class="headerlink" title="2 青龙"></a>2 青龙</h1><p>Docker-qinglong:<a href="https://hub.docker.com/r/whyour/qinglong">whyour&#x2F;qinglong - Docker Image | Docker Hub</a></p>
<h2 id="2-1-安装"><a href="#2-1-安装" class="headerlink" title="2.1 安装"></a>2.1 安装</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">拉取 qinglong 镜像</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo docker pull whyour/qinglong</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">启动容器（端口映射：-p 前面的是服务器端口，后面的是容器端口）</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo docker run -dit \</span><br><span class="line">  -v $PWD/ql1:/ql/data \</span><br><span class="line">  -p 5701:5700 \</span><br><span class="line">  --name ql1 \</span><br><span class="line">  --hostname ql1 \</span><br><span class="line">  --restart unless-stopped \</span><br><span class="line">  whyour/qinglong:latest</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">访问 http://10.1.16.116:5701/ 配置青龙</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>





<h2 id="2-2-拉取脚本并配置"><a href="#2-2-拉取脚本并配置" class="headerlink" title="2.2 拉取脚本并配置"></a>2.2 拉取脚本并配置</h2><h1 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h1><h2 id="1-Zerotier-1"><a href="#1-Zerotier-1" class="headerlink" title="1 Zerotier"></a>1 Zerotier</h2><h2 id="2-qinglong"><a href="#2-qinglong" class="headerlink" title="2 qinglong"></a>2 qinglong</h2><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/apple_54531770/article/details/124236904?spm=1001.2101.3001.6650.3&utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-2~default~CTRLIST~Rate-3-124236904-blog-125535606.235%5Ev31%5Epc_relevant_default_base3&depth_1-utm_source=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-2~default~CTRLIST~Rate-3-124236904-blog-125535606.235%5Ev31%5Epc_relevant_default_base3&utm_relevant_index=6">(125条消息) ELM饿了么获取COOKIE教程附吃货豆脚本_饿了么cookie_掉进电商坑三年没爬出来的东叔的博客-CSDN博客</a></p>
